{"tid":2196760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國首次！波特蘭禁止商家使用臉部辨識 保障個人隱私權","createTime":"2020-09-10T06:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T06:38:55.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56f9c31a19b97def584703728d3273f325a0d236","tid":2196760,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:36:16.000Z","msg":"美國首次！波特蘭禁止商家使用臉部辨識 保障個人隱私權<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3287363\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287363&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGEyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=459fc9a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287363&h=ca8a7bef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3287363</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國俄勒岡州波特蘭市議會（Portland）於9日投票通過，禁止私人企業或商家使用使用臉部辨識系統，保護個人的隱私權，波特蘭也是在公共場所運用臉部辨識的爭議中，首個發出禁令的城市。<br />\n<br />\n根據《路透》報導，波特蘭市議會也通過，禁止公部門採購或使用臉部辨識系統，美國包括舊金山和奧克蘭的一些城市，先前也禁止政府使用臉部辨識。<br />\n<br />\n臉部辨識系統可以比對現有資料庫，快速地從照片和影片中辨識出個人身分，在近幾年中受到私人企業和警察的青睞，但反對人士認為，該技術侵犯個人隱私，並且加劇種族和性別偏見。<br />\n<br />\n美國公民自由聯盟表示，希望在波特蘭通過此禁令後，能夠刺激俄勒岡州當局全面禁止使用臉部辨識技術。"},{"pid":"d4621930ef724cbe61fc3f9e565a18255ead134b","tid":2196760,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eceb4895ef9262b9e18bef0a1fc4403e880da2b6","tid":2196760,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:38:55.000Z","msg":"portland唔係loot緊咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}